<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 06:10:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国家官员担心国际刑事法院可能指控以色列在加沙犯有种族灭绝罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/state-officials-fear-hauge-could-charge-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza/0000018c-c1a9-d3e0-abac-d9a9acd80000</link><description>国际法院在制定国际法方面具有巨大影响力。国际法专家雪莉·阿维夫·耶尼 (Shelly Aviv Yeini) 博士表示，承认南非的主张可能会加深人们对以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的看法。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 04:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/state-officials-fear-hauge-could-charge-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza/0000018c-c1a9-d3e0-abac-d9a9acd80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部地区拉响警报迎接新年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-live/israel-brings-in-the-new-year-with-sirens-across-central-israel/0000018c-c318-d4e1-ad8f-ffb949720000</link><description>据伊拉克军队消息人士称，无人机在伊拉克艾因阿萨德基地上空被拦截 ■ 以色列国防军表示，拦截了从叙利亚进入以色列领土的空中目标 ■ 美国国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比：“我们并不是在寻求与胡塞武装发生冲突” ” ■ MDA，以色列警方报告称，约旦河西岸定居点附近发生刺伤事件，两人受轻伤。 ■ 火箭弹袭击以色列北部后，以色列对黎巴嫩和叙利亚发动袭击。 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙至少有 133 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 21,822 人死亡、56,451 人受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 04:14:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-live/israel-brings-in-the-new-year-with-sirens-across-central-israel/0000018c-c318-d4e1-ad8f-ffb949720000</guid></item><item><title>与以色列的全面战争可能损害真主党的政治利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/full-blown-israel-war-could-harm-hezbollahs-political-interests/0000018c-c194-d6c4-ab8d-e1b4c2eb0000</link><description>由于黎巴嫩面临金融危机，数万名以农业为主要收入来源的黎巴嫩人撤离了黎巴嫩南部的村庄。黎巴嫩最高马龙派基督教精神权威表示：“我们不希望战争蔓延到黎巴嫩南部。”作为政府的一部分，真主党必须表明它正在为本国的国家利益而努力</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 04:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/full-blown-israel-war-could-harm-hezbollahs-political-interests/0000018c-c194-d6c4-ab8d-e1b4c2eb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警探被控七月袭击反政府抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-detective-charged-with-assaulting-anti-government-protester-in-july/0000018c-c180-d3e0-abac-d9a99deb0000</link><description>德克尔·拉齐米（Dekel Lazimi）殴打了一名被束缚且没有拒捕的抗议者。 《国土报》拍摄了这一事件。抗议者说：“我很清楚，如果没有记录下来，他们就不会相信我。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 23:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-detective-charged-with-assaulting-anti-government-protester-in-july/0000018c-c180-d3e0-abac-d9a99deb0000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年是以色列自 1950 年开始记录以来最热的年份之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-one-of-israels-hottest-years-since-keeping-of-records-began-in-1950/0000018c-c181-d3e0-abac-d9a948f60000</link><description>根据以色列气象局的年度总结，2023年5月下旬和6月发生了四次异常降雨事件，7月和8月出现了持续且异常的热浪，11月和12月出现了异常大雨。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 23:22:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-one-of-israels-hottest-years-since-keeping-of-records-began-in-1950/0000018c-c181-d3e0-abac-d9a948f60000</guid></item><item><title>2024 年前夕，反内塔尼亚胡抗议者对 10 月 7 日的事件感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-31/ty-article/.highlight/on-the-eve-of-2024-anti-netanyahu-protesters-are-fueled-with-rage-over-october-7/0000018c-c08c-d6c4-ab8d-e1bc94de0000</link><description>虽然之前的司法政变抗议传递的信息是对未来潜在损害的警告，但现在由于内塔尼亚胡未能保护国家，已经付出了血腥的代价</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 19:49:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-31/ty-article/.highlight/on-the-eve-of-2024-anti-netanyahu-protesters-are-fueled-with-rage-over-october-7/0000018c-c08c-d6c4-ab8d-e1bc94de0000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统沙斯党推动法案推迟最高法院对司法政变法的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-shas-party-pushing-bill-to-delay-top-court-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c148-d3e0-abac-d9e974ae0000</link><description>根据该法案，退休的最高法院法官将被允许在退休后九个月内公布剩余裁决，而不是像现在这样三个月</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 19:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-shas-party-pushing-bill-to-delay-top-court-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c148-d3e0-abac-d9e974ae0000</guid></item><item><title>12 个步骤、4 个零日漏洞、1 个零点击：美国如何入侵 iPhone 来监视俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/12-steps-4-zero-clicks-how-the-u-s-hacked-the-iphone-to-spy-on-russia/0000018c-c0cd-d3e0-abac-d8ed05e00000</link><description>在黑客大会上，俄罗斯网络公司揭露了有史以来最复杂的黑客攻击之一，据称美国利用这些攻击来监视他们以及中国、叙利亚甚至以色列的官员；与此同时，印度莫迪呼吁苹果公司透露新的 Pegasus 目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 18:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/12-steps-4-zero-clicks-how-the-u-s-hacked-the-iphone-to-spy-on-russia/0000018c-c0cd-d3e0-abac-d8ed05e00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的医疗报告显示身体状况良好，没有心脏异常</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-medical-report-shows-good-condition-no-cardiac-anomalies/0000018c-c08f-d3e0-abac-d8afcdeb0000</link><description>报告发布三天前，一名平民要求以色列总检察长公开内塔尼亚胡的健康状况，认为隐瞒这一情况会使允许宣布总理不适合任职的《基本法》失效。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 18:15:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-medical-report-shows-good-condition-no-cardiac-anomalies/0000018c-c08f-d3e0-abac-d8afcdeb0000</guid></item><item><title>比比和拜登，兄弟情谊的对立面：《国土报》关于 2023 年美以关系的重要报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-timeline/.premium/bibi-and-biden-the-anti-bromance-key-haaretz-stories-on-u-s-israel-relations-in-2023/0000018c-c021-d4e1-ad8f-fcb1a1920000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 17:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-timeline/.premium/bibi-and-biden-the-anti-bromance-key-haaretz-stories-on-u-s-israel-relations-in-2023/0000018c-c021-d4e1-ad8f-fcb1a1920000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年是以色列有史以来最糟糕的一年。它以一些希望的痕迹结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-israels-worst-year-ever-it-ends-with-a-few-traces-of-hope/0000018c-c043-d4e1-ad8f-fcf349300000</link><description>这是以色列最命运的一年，内忧外患的矛盾暴露和加剧了国家的核心矛盾。人们第一次对以色列是否能够继续遏制这些矛盾产生重大疑问——但一切都还没有结束</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 16:28:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-israels-worst-year-ever-it-ends-with-a-few-traces-of-hope/0000018c-c043-d4e1-ad8f-fcf349300000</guid></item><item><title>真主党副领袖表示以色列必须停止加沙战争才能结束黎巴嫩的战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-israel-must-stop-gaza-war-for-combat-in-lebanon-to-end/0000018c-c066-d6c4-ab8d-e1f600220000</link><description>据报道，美国调解员阿莫斯·霍赫斯坦将很快访问黎巴嫩，试图安排停火。以色列总理内塔尼亚胡表示，“如果我们不能通过外交实现我们的目标，我们将通过军事手段实现”</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 15:56:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-israel-must-stop-gaza-war-for-combat-in-lebanon-to-end/0000018c-c066-d6c4-ab8d-e1f600220000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列精神卫生系统面临崩溃，数十名精神科医生前往英国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-system-in-israel-collapses-psychiatrists-are-leaving-for-britain/0000018c-c026-d3e0-abac-d8af89aa0000</link><description>消息人士将人才外流归因于工作量不断增加，并认为情况只会恶化，因为卫生部修复该系统的计划仍在等待财政部的资金批准</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 15:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-system-in-israel-collapses-psychiatrists-are-leaving-for-britain/0000018c-c026-d3e0-abac-d8af89aa0000</guid></item><item><title>一名加沙男孩梦想打破互联网。他做到了——在以色列炸弹炸死他之后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/a-gaza-boy-dreamed-of-breaking-the-internet-he-did-after-an-israeli-bomb-killed-him/0000018c-bfcb-d4e1-ad8f-bffbc01b0000</link><description>13 岁的 Awni Eldous 经营着一个 YouTube 频道，梦想成为一名有影响力的人。他的故事在世界各地引起共鸣，代表了加沙儿童在战争中的悲剧</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 14:48:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/a-gaza-boy-dreamed-of-breaking-the-internet-he-did-after-an-israeli-bomb-killed-him/0000018c-bfcb-d4e1-ad8f-bffbc01b0000</guid></item><item><title>“100-20万，而不是200万”：以色列财政部长设想加沙人口减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/100-200-000-not-two-million-israels-finance-minister-envisions-depopulated-gaza/0000018c-bfe8-d6c4-ab8d-fffc0b910000</link><description>以色列极右翼财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇与越来越多的高级立法者一起表示支持大规模转移加沙平民，以解决以色列战后安全问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 14:46:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/100-200-000-not-two-million-israels-finance-minister-envisions-depopulated-gaza/0000018c-bfe8-d6c4-ab8d-fffc0b910000</guid></item><item><title>美国对以色列的支持就没有红线吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/are-there-no-red-lines-to-u-s-support-for-israel/0000018c-bf3a-d45c-a98e-bf7ea92b0000</link><description>10月7日是一起令人发指的罪行。但是，有多少加沙人必须死去，有多少以色列部长必须推动种族清洗，内塔尼​​亚胡必须否认多少失败——美国才能重新考虑其对以色列政府发动的邪恶战争的不道德、无条件的支持？</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/are-there-no-red-lines-to-u-s-support-for-israel/0000018c-bf3a-d45c-a98e-bf7ea92b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争，以色列内阁投票决定将地方选举推迟至二月下旬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-votes-to-delay-local-elections-until-late-february-due-to-gaza-war/0000018c-bffd-d6c4-ab8d-fffd56ab0000</link><description>以色列国防军数据显示，数百名候选人在预备役中服役，无法被释放，选举第二次推迟，但代表预备役候选人的律师表示，推迟选举“具有讽刺意味的是，这增加了对手的优势”</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-votes-to-delay-local-elections-until-late-february-due-to-gaza-war/0000018c-bffd-d6c4-ab8d-fffd56ab0000</guid></item><item><title>赛车无人机军备竞赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/the-racing-drones-arms-race/0000018c-bf91-d6c4-ab8d-ffb5243a0000</link><description>FPV 无人机凭借 150 公里/小时的疯狂机动性，已成为乌克兰战场上精确、致命的制导武器。对他们的防御是有限的。他们很快就会出现在我们的舞台上吗？以色列准备好了吗？</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/the-racing-drones-arms-race/0000018c-bf91-d6c4-ab8d-ffb5243a0000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争而延长学年，大多数以色列大学都开始学年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/following-delays-academic-school-year-begins-at-most-israeli-universities/0000018c-bfd3-d6c4-ab8d-fff7a61a0000</link><description>课程于周日开始，比原计划晚了大约两个半月，并且没有预备役人员。 ■ 学术机构与军队之间达成的一项协议，为仍在预备役的 58,000 名学生和教师制定了调整框架</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 13:15:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/following-delays-academic-school-year-begins-at-most-israeli-universities/0000018c-bfd3-d6c4-ab8d-fff7a61a0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-bfd2-d4e1-ad8f-bff360880000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，自10月7日以来，以色列士兵在战斗中丧生的人数为506人</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 12:55:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-bfd2-d4e1-ad8f-bff360880000</guid></item></channel></rss>